metadata.name: To the light
metadata.description:
To look forward
To believe
To be patient
To breathe calmly
To be persistent
To be beautiful
To become love
To become kindness
To become the one who thrives
on peace, love, compassion
To become with the one and only

I am ready
I am loyal
I am faith
I am resilient
I am the light~

Poetry by Ashwini Dodani
